photo.description: Pretty pleased with this one, despite the fact that it's basically impossible to take a novel picture of this hugely popular cathedral. We climbed to the top of this tower, up a tiny spiral staircase containing 50% air to 50% fat guy sweat vapour. Not pleasant. Fact: it took 600 years to complete construction. Cowboy builders for you.
